<tr id="L358"><td><a href="#L358">358</a></td><td>KIRK:  The Horta is intelligent, peaceful, mild. She had no objection to sharing this planet with you, till you broke into her nursery and started destroying her eggs. Then she fought back in the only way she knew how, as any mother would fight when her children are in danger.</td></tr>

