<tr id="L371"><td><a href="#L371">371</a></td><td>KIRK:  Well, Spock, I'm going to have to ask you to get in touch with the Horta again. Tell her our proposition. She and her children can do all the tunnelling they want. Our people will remove the minerals, and each side will leave the other alone. Think she'll go for it?</td></tr>

